  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      21 patients were randomised to receive instructions and coaching or no intervention on the
      use and intake of ganciclovir. Intake of medication was measured by an electronic pill box.
      The duration of the study was 100 days.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
